header.title: General Notes
header.content:
Welcome to the Parefull API docs! These are the public endpoints available for use. Some paths use JWT since they are admin or utility only.

Notes

  • You can use Postman to test the API with this Postman collection file
  • Staging and Development API urls are different than what is listed in the main API docs.
  • Please submit any questions/comments as emails to aarondllc@gmail.com

API dependencies

  • JTW (Json web tokens) for protected routes https://github.com/auth0/node-jsonwebtoken
